  "title": "BRAIN",
  "description": "One brain. Two sides. Left and Right. Together, they should be a perfect team—but today, they’re a disaster. From Blair Moro (Cabaret of Murder), BRAIN is a fast, funny, and wildly unpredictable comedy about the mind’s greatest struggle: itself. “Expertly directed.” – A. Wade “Brilliant.” – J. Marley",
